    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s totally ready for a new home. If you're looking for something reliable and ready to hit the road without any fuss, this is the one for you. I've taken great care of it, and it's got plenty of life left for its next adventure. Let me know if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
