    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sustained aesthetic appeal. This specimen has been meticulously curated to ensure a refined driving experience, maintaining the high standards expected of a professional-grade asset. The interior remains remarkably preserved, while the powertrain delivers consistent, reliable performance. A premier selection for the sophisticated driver seeking a harmonious balance of value and prestige.",
