    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. Whether you're cruising around town or heading out on a road trip, it handles beautifully and feels great behind the wheel. It's clean, well-cared for, and ready for a new home. I'd love for you to come check it out and see for yourself\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
